Gene to Symbol Mappings

Source: R/AllGenerics.R, R/methods-gene2symbol.R

Gene to Symbol Mappings

gene2symbol(object)

# S4 method for SummarizedExperiment
gene2symbol(object)

Arguments

object

Object.

Value

data.frame containing gene identifier and gene name (aka symbol) mappings.

See also

Other Data Functions: flatFiles, sampleDirs, uniteInterestingGroups
